collectionMetadata.name: SLA Master Tenants
collectionMetadata.description:
This layer captures the tenancy details concerning Master Tenants of State properties under SLA's management who have obtained in-principle approval to sublet certain State properties.

Users should view refer to SLA's website at http://www.sla.gov.sg under <Rental of State Property and Land> on advice for prospective sub-tenants before using the dataset.
